      "writtenOn": "2016-05-04T18:21:22Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yep, pushes are triggered by drag and drop, and we explicitly wanted to support adding to copy-in-progress, as that\u0027s what users expect for any copy operation.\n\neasonj/birenbaum can say more on this.",
      "parentUuid": "6d7da3ec_1d9a9fd4",
