      "writtenOn": "2016-05-04T18:33:35Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Considering many people probably do not currently use this feature, it may be possible to ease that restriction. However, as of now, it is possible to add more files to be copied while another copy is in flight, and the progress indicator should update appropriately. Glad to talk to J if we think that\u0027s unnecessary / unreasonable.",
      "parentUuid": "6d7da3ec_4f0a9e7a",
